nodes.text: Jennie Lee Taggar was a starfighter pilot with the Rebel Alliance. She flew a Y-wing at the Battle of Endor. She died while attacking a Star Destroyer.
She had a son named Rone Taggar, who became a pilot with the New Republic, and would later name his Recon-X starfighter after her, the Jennie Lee.
Jennie Lee Taggar's name is inferred from the name of the Jennie Lee.
